{"tid":1226604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日唔該大家 照出黎！","createTime":"2019-06-15T12:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T16:16:23.000Z","uid":139193,"like":1873,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"746cf87493650e4097c940d572968415f896d23d","tid":1226604,"uid":139193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:22:27.000Z","msg":"雖然星期一三罷取消 <br />\n但聽日依然要出<br />\n我地仲未贏<br />\n啲義士仲未獲釋<br />\n啲黑警仲未被清算<br />\n如果林鄭講句暫緩你地就信<br />\n聽日少曬人出<br />\n只會比共產黨知道香港人係幾咁易呃<br />\n咁共產黨下一步只會更猖狂<br />\n更何況<br />\n如果咁就收貨<br />\n你對唔對得住612中槍被捕嘅人<br />\n對唔對得住果日出去奮鬥嘅自己<br />\n約定你聽日 不撤不散"},{"pid":"8922de01ec6748c5ad38f83b87a5245f699e9cec","tid":1226604,"uid":259302,"like":142,"dislike":2,"score":140,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:23:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1.撤回修例<br />\n2.收回示威是爆動的定性<br />\n3.釋放所有過去一週因示威被捕的人<br />\n4.追究警方使用過份武力，甚至暴力<br />\n若明天和平遊行有人叫「林鄭下台」「打倒中共」「港獨」等無關上述四點的口號，請勿理會。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"22c659707299e28f051b3f6bd42c845d7ad8cf13","tid":1226604,"uid":139193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:35:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d472107ae3c96d01d1f2a05ef2b76f24de420466","tid":1226604,"uid":139193,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:35:40.000Z","msg":"聽日唔出<br />\n以後就無機會！"},{"pid":"c4b41585c832aad57a257baea3967b20e2f2cce7","tid":1226604,"uid":139193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:36:06.000Z","msg":"香港人 無咪咁怕麻煩？"},{"pid":"efd80944b359fa770ecd67d85c7b49b6b65e2475","tid":1226604,"uid":2300,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:36:12.000Z","msg":"會照出"},{"pid":"376ed5d9658c316bc83c75f643f30f5b2a69cc6e","tid":1226604,"uid":139193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:36:20.000Z","msg":"一個下晝嘅時間都無？"},{"pid":"41e80c8da4761d3ef90d8b26cede546c7acc82c3","tid":1226604,"uid":139193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c