oji\" />你地個個post都講但又唔講when and where叫人地點出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211a6562fd067f08fa4a5decde3a5d8eccc322b5","tid":1226604,"uid":169178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:44:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"768a7a94cb6efadcc1402bf2e3ad45b8e01b02f8","tid":1226604,"uid":18296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11cae15f32c9506a35847b31d52d355dad688f79","tid":1226604,"uid":139193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"486145f46aaaca3ef7457feea2ab828af20b3903","tid":1226604,"uid":2424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:47:20.000Z","msg":"聽日邊度行到邊度？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:48:07.000Z","msg":"1430開始 維園行到金鐘添美道"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:44:23.000Z","msg":"睇到了，thanks! 一定出"},{"pid":"5e16d87b5e19d0d5c2cce35e6970723b23fba301","tid":1226604,"uid":28170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:46:58.000Z","msg":"【逃犯條例】反俢例黃衣男太古廣場危站五小時墮地 市民：撐住呀<br />\n特首林鄭月娥剛宣布暫緩《逃犯條例》修例工作，收回二讀預告，隨即便有人在6月12日爆發激烈衝突的金鐘太古廣場危站，其身旁掛有一幅寫著「反送中」的橫額。今日（15日）下午4時半，一名男子於金鐘道88號太古廣場正進行維修的停車場平台危站，他身穿黃衣外套，寫有抗議字句，其旁邊棚架上掛起「反送中No Extradition To China」的橫額，上面亦寫有「全面撤回送中，我們不是暴動，釋放學生傷者，林鄭下台，Help Hong Kong」的訴求標語。警方封鎖金鐘道西行兩條行車線以處理事件，而消防亦到場在金鐘道地面開氣墊戒備。<br />\n<br />\n至下午該名黃衣人仍未返回安全位置，背向馬路站著，立法會議員鄺俊宇聞訊趕至了解，並於對面馬路用揚聲器呼籲黃衣人轉身，希望與黃衣人對話。另外有數名市民於現場唱起《Sing hallelujah to the Lord》詩歌，現場消息指，警方談判專家亦已到場。至晚上8時半，該名男子脫下黃衣，在平台位置坐下休息，持盾警及帶同繩索的消防員於樓上戒備。現場消息指，男子手持一把鎅刀，談判專家曾上前與男子溝通但男子不願多談，警員過程中有遞水給男子。至近9時許，男子突然往外爬出棚架，其間4名消防員嘗試將男子拉回不果，男子上衣被拉脫後突然墮下，其後倒臥地上，消防員正為男子進行心外壓搶救，有在場市民高叫男子「撐住呀！」，男子被送上救護車搶救。"},{"pid":"703800b0b50130174caa235a9cd5148bd936783c","tid":1226604,"uid":23481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:47:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>[不撤不散］616集氣區！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1226467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1226467</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8269d78c0c6a9198ae455d0985fa5cd621c7d1c9","tid":1226604,"uid":80139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:47:18.000Z","msg":"不撤不散"},{"pid":"2e79337b53b15e4328df9cb4b102ba1d9ebede6e","tid":1226604,"uid":255690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"係香港人就聽日點都出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dab68c51800cb9c50ce81816860bda3f59713dd","tid":1226604,"uid":220057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:53:56.000Z","msg":"香港要自救"},{"pid":"202bd4dc14b39edd4b3a978f1e00bf72f7eaacff","tid":1226604,"uid":239399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:56:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca9185b8c9e59934e41327a4403fac2211ef988a","tid":1226604,"uid":246083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:56:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cd789f013b270c706bfff416b00326ef1e4ab52","tid":1226604,"uid":93935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c35cc6554641c715aa818cef8f13963c3fee12","tid":1226604,"uid":139193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b8586344f3f196c7a1e57911d11aa0cf5b701ea","tid":1226604,"uid":229801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:38:46.000Z","msg":"今日777講野前去咗買物資，諗住聽日行完放低。<br />\n依家咁環境，聽日啲物資仲令唔令去好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:57:26.000Z","msg":"照拎"},{"pid":"a071dd73d3162e1af4063d52be932bf519f02c21","tid":1226604,"uid":139193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:57:45.000Z","msg":"場仗未打完"},{"pid":"03de076282b236c24ebd68f37c7c623e699f951e","tid":1226604,"uid":139193,"like":0,"dislike"